The 3 tales are made from "1000 English basic words"
(https://en.wiktionary.org/w/index.php?title=Category:1000_English_basic_words&pageuntil=daughter#mw-pages)
but it has 3 more words.
These are:
-pirate
-whiskey
-vodka
They're suitable for 6-10 years old boys (girls won't like them).
You can find 15 triplets in Zsolti's tale.
You can find 8 triplets in Thomas's tale.
You can find 13 triplets in Roland's tale.
